# bin/

Command-line executable scripts for the Intent CLI tool. Each script implements a specific command or functionality, with a clear separation of concerns: configuration helpers, project initialization, command routing, and feature implementations like steel thread management, treeindex generation, and Backlog integration.

## Files

- `intent` -- Main entry point and command router; dispatches to subcommands and handles global flags
- `intent_treeindex` -- Generate `.treeindex` directory summaries using Claude AI with fingerprint-based staleness detection
- `intent_st` -- Manage steel threads; create, list, show, edit, repair, and organize steel thread directories
- `intent_config` -- Shared JSON configuration library; provides config loading, parsing, and project root detection
- `intent_helpers` -- Utility functions for version management and YAML-to-JSON migration
- `intent_init` -- Initialize new Intent v2.0.0 projects with directory structure and config
- `intent_backlog` -- Wrapper for Backlog.md task management integration with Intent workflows
- `intent_bl` -- Shorthand alias for `intent_backlog`
- `intent_doctor` -- Diagnose and fix Intent configuration issues
- `intent_help` -- Display help for Intent commands with command-specific documentation
- `intent_info` -- Show Intent installation and project information (status, steel threads, counts)
- `intent_status` -- Sync steel thread status with Backlog task completion
- `intent_task` -- Manage Backlog tasks linked to steel threads
- `intent_migrate` -- Migrate embedded tasks from steel threads to Backlog.md
- `intent_organise` -- Organize steel threads by status into directory structure
- `intent_llm` -- Manage LLM prompts and context files; display usage rules
- `intent_bootstrap` -- Initial Intent setup for first-time users; creates config and directories
- `intent_upgrade` -- Upgrade STP projects to Intent v2.3.4 with migration and backup
- `intent_main` -- Backward compatibility wrapper for `stp` command (aliases to intent)
- `intent_minimal` -- Minimal Intent wrapper for Phase 1 testing
